- Don't go.

573
00:46:46,720 --> 00:46:48,120
I'll see you later.

574
00:46:48,590 --> 00:46:49,720
Bye.

575
00:46:50,360 --> 00:46:53,060
- See you next time, then.
- Sure.

576
00:46:58,370 --> 00:46:59,930
Be careful in the snow!

577
00:47:43,180 --> 00:47:46,280
Why are you back so early?

578
00:47:46,420 --> 00:47:49,580
