Just wanted something simple.

586
00:48:30,630 --> 00:48:31,930
It's good, huh?

587
00:48:35,130 --> 00:48:38,330
If you could stop time,
what would you do first?

588
00:48:40,400 --> 00:48:45,400
If everyone else is frozen
and only you can move?

589
00:48:46,580 --> 00:48:49,880
If time stopped, you wouldn't die.

590
00:48:52,920 --> 00:48:54,710
Don't you want to live?

591
00:48:59,090 --> 00:49:00,850
