doesn't come, I wait.

613
00:50:48,270 --> 00:50:50,860
Do you wonder about every patient?

614
00:50:51,540 --> 00:50:53,060
Well...

615
00:50:54,310 --> 00:50:58,210
You're blushing. It's love all right.

616
00:51:00,210 --> 00:51:01,680
Hey, KANG Chul-kyu!

617
00:51:01,780 --> 00:51:03,340
