630
00:51:58,500 --> 00:52:00,530
Under one condition.

631
00:52:07,140 --> 00:52:09,080
Now, what.

632
00:52:09,910 --> 00:52:12,180
I'll tell you after I break it off.

633
00:52:12,680 --> 00:52:14,880
A promise is a promise.

634
00:52:30,000 --> 00:52:33,600
Since when was it no smoking in here.

635
00:52:36,770 --> 00:52:38,570
No idea.

636
