I lose touch altogether.

751
01:08:17,950 --> 01:08:20,710
I had one more condition. Remember?

752
01:08:23,720 --> 01:08:25,520
What is it?

753
01:08:48,410 --> 01:08:50,540
Please die at my side.

754
01:08:57,990 --> 01:09:01,250
