759
01:09:22,110 --> 01:09:28,380
I'll charge it and call you back later.

760
01:09:28,550 --> 01:09:29,950
Bye.

761
01:09:29,950 --> 01:09:31,250
Hi.

762
01:09:35,760 --> 01:09:39,390
