Ah, Vitamin ABC. It
helps me get smarter.

820
01:22:20,860 --> 01:22:23,980
Where'd you get these pills?

821
01:22:24,460 --> 01:22:26,660
They're my friends' pills.

822
01:22:27,360 --> 01:22:31,820
Since when did your
friend start taking this?

823
01:22:32,740 --> 01:22:34,260
Why?

824
01:22:34,940 --> 01:22:39,240
The pain must've been
severe to take these pills.

825
01:22:40,710 --> 01:22:41,800
What?

826
01:22:42,340 --> 01:22:47,870
They're painkillers for
patients with cancer or leukemia.

827
01:22:48,180 --> 01:22:50,240
Terminal patients.

828
01:22:51,550 --> 01:22:55,290
Have you heard of
the hospice ward?

829
01:22:56,230 --> 01:23:00,030
It's where dying patients stay...

830
01:23:00,460 --> 01:23:04,520
with consent from their families.

831
01:23:19,520 --> 01:23:20,780
Mom!

832
01:23:20,920 --> 01:23:23,520
Watch the house while we're out.

833
01:23:23,520 --> 01:23:25,920
See you later, sis!

834
01:23:32,090 --> 01:23:33,530
No!

835
01:23:58,250 --> 01:24:01,310
When I found out what
Vitamin ABC really was...

836
01:24:01,560 --> 01:24:05,430
When I finally realized
what they were...

837
01:24:05,660 --> 01:24:10,220
When my whole world
turned pitch dark before me...

838
01:24:10,670 --> 01:24:12,130
What's wrong?

839
01:24:12,370 --> 01:24:15,060
I died before K.

840
01:24:17,970 --> 01:24:25,710
I met K a year after my
whole family passed away.

841
01:24:27,450 --> 01:24:31,440
Though almost 3 hours passed...

842
01:24:32,790 --> 01:24:35,880
he stood there frozen like stone.

843
01:24:36,130 --> 01:24:39,730
Crying and looking in the
direction his mother went.

844
01:24:39,730 --> 01:24:44,530
This will be enough to support you
till you're an adult, Chul-kyu.

845
01:24:45,600 --> 01:24:51,700
He looked sadder
and more hurt than me.

846
01:24:53,140 --> 01:24:55,940
He needed a hug
more than me.

847
01:24:56,950 --> 01:24:59,210
Is there anything you want to tell me?

848
01:24:59,980 --> 01:25:01,510
Like what?

849
01:25:04,690 --> 01:25:08,380
A deep, dark secret?

850
01:25:11,060 --> 01:25:14,620
Say anything. I'm ready to listen.

851
01:25:16,230 --> 01:25:17,660
I like you.

852
01:25:17,970 --> 01:25:20,600
Stupid idiot.

853
01:25:21,200 --> 01:25:23,000
Do you have a wish?

854
01:25:23,110 --> 01:25:24,670
What's with you?

855
01:25:24,670 --> 01:25:27,800
Just curious all of a sudden.

856
01:25:29,550 --> 01:25:33,310
If you could do anything
you want in the world.

857
01:25:33,920 --> 01:25:35,910
K is dying.

858
01:25:36,250 --> 01:25:38,720
Meet a great guy and get married.

859
01:25:38,890 --> 01:25:40,760
Can't I marry you?

860
01:25:40,760 --> 01:25:42,950
I'm not a great guy.

861
01:25:43,130 --> 01:25:45,430
Then who is?

862
01:25:45,430 --> 01:25:49,330
Someone who is healthy and nice.

863
01:25:49,900 --> 01:25:52,390
Who knows how to take
care of his family.

864
01:25:53,600 --> 01:25:56,800
I already met a great guy.

865
01:25:57,640 --> 01:26:01,300
But K told me to
meet someone else.

866
01:26:01,780 --> 01:26:05,270
He said that was his wish.

867
01:26:06,850 --> 01:26:10,790
KANG Chul-kyu

868
01:26:14,460 --> 01:26:17,550
When I heard K fainted...

869
01:26:18,060 --> 01:26:21,830
I rushed over,
afraid I'll go crazy.

870
01:26:23,500 --> 01:26:25,300
But I...

871
01:26:26,240 --> 01:26:27,840
... couldn't even go crazy.

872
01:26:27,840 --> 01:26:29,840
No, doc.

873
01:26:29,840 --> 01:26:32,500
But she should know.

874
01:26:33,480 --> 01:26:35,970
What are you going to do?

875
01:26:36,680 --> 01:26:38,740
I don't know.

876
01:26:43,150 --> 01:26:46,050
It feels like a needle
stuck in my throat.

877
01:26:49,390 --> 01:26:51,120
Right here.

878
01:26:52,900 --> 01:26:55,020
It gets stuck right here.

879
01:26:56,500 --> 01:26:59,130
I can't say it.

880
01:27:00,840 --> 01:27:07,640
She'll live on. Think of yourself.

881
01:27:08,440 --> 01:27:10,840
She's different.

882
01:27:12,180 --> 01:27:14,270
She needs someone beside her.

883
01:27:29,600 --> 01:27:32,090
- Hello.
- There goes Mr. Perfect.

884
01:27:33,400 --> 01:27:35,800
Glowing from head to toe!

885
01:27:40,640 --> 01:27:42,910
I picked a man.

886
01:27:52,690 --> 01:27:54,850
Which side did you drink from?

887
01:27:57,960 --> 01:27:59,190
Pardon?

888
01:27:59,190 --> 01:28:01,590
I'm engaged.

889
01:28:02,130 --> 01:28:09,500
Stupid. You think I care
whether you're engaged or not?

890
01:28:10,810 --> 01:28:14,400
Just play along and
meet me. For K.

891
01:28:15,480 --> 01:28:17,500
Am I a bitch?

892
01:28:18,210 --> 01:28:20,720
I don't have time
to worry about that!

893
01:28:20,720 --> 01:28:23,080
The man I love is dying!

894
01:28:33,960 --> 01:28:39,760
If I could be born again...
A ring? A pair of glasses?

895
01:28:41,470 --> 01:28:45,570
A bed? A diary?

896
01:28:46,040 --> 01:28:49,740
Born again as things like
that? What fun is that?

897
01:28:50,010 --> 01:28:54,640
You can buy me. It'll
always be fun at your side.

898
01:29:10,670 --> 01:29:14,470
What's wrong? Are you okay?

899
01:29:16,570 --> 01:29:17,830
Let me see your hand.

900
01:29:25,210 --> 01:29:26,700
Where are you going?

901
01:29:46,440 --> 01:29:48,400
I made a deal with myself.

902
01:29:49,140 --> 01:29:51,610
If he turns around,
I'd tell him everything.

903
01:29:53,140 --> 01:29:57,510
If he turns around, I'd
hug him and stop everything.

904
01:29:59,250 --> 01:30:02,240
But K didn't look back.

905
01:30:03,590 --> 01:30:07,040
And there was nothing
I could do.

906
01:30:12,730 --> 01:30:15,200
Why are you eating
noodles instead of rice?

907
01:30:16,160 --> 01:30:18,360
Just wanted something simple.

908
01:30:21,870 --> 01:30:24,460
- It's good, huh?
- Yeah.

909
01:30:28,540 --> 01:30:31,640
As I sat eating the
noodles with him...

910
01:30:32,810 --> 01:30:35,220
I'd think, 'Don't
die you bastard'

911
01:30:35,220 --> 01:30:38,080
and drank some water instead.

912
01:30:38,590 --> 01:30:43,350
'Tell me. Let me hold you!
I'll die with you! '

913
01:30:43,690 --> 01:30:48,150
'I'll follow you and pay you back
for everything you did for me! '

914
01:30:48,960 --> 01:30:52,160
Instead, I just drank the water.

915
01:30:53,200 --> 01:30:55,830
And finished the noodles.

916
01:31:00,010 --> 01:31:05,640
There's only one holder,
but many toothbrushes.

917
01:31:07,250 --> 01:31:10,050
What's that got to do with marriage?

918
01:31:10,920 --> 01:31:17,480
Being together as one like
toothbrushes in a holder.

919
01:31:21,260 --> 01:31:23,560
Then I must be married, already.

920
01:31:25,030 --> 01:31:28,900
Stupid! You can't be
married without a wedding.

921
01:31:30,910 --> 01:31:32,400
Really?

922
01:32:02,600 --> 01:32:05,000
Can we get married, soon?

923
01:32:30,430 --> 01:32:33,160
Wait out there. I'll
try on something else.

924
01:33:09,640 --> 01:33:11,730
The hell you...

925
01:33:14,740 --> 01:33:17,540
Who says you can do
whatever you want with me!

926
01:33:27,890 --> 01:33:29,480
I'm sorry.

927
01:33:36,130 --> 01:33:39,160
I want to tell him I love him.

928
01:33:39,570 --> 01:33:43,940
I want to open my mouth
and say I love him.

929
01:33:45,410 --> 01:33:49,280
But I knew tears will fall
before I could say it.

930
01:33:49,610 --> 01:33:53,010
So I kept silent, again.

931
01:34:06,390 --> 01:34:08,590
When are you going to talk to me?

932
01:34:10,100 --> 01:34:14,590
Didn't you hear me screaming
at you all this time?

933
01:34:15,200 --> 01:34:16,640
What?

934
01:34:18,140 --> 01:34:19,800
Stupid.

935
01:34:20,540 --> 01:34:22,480
I didn't hear anything.

936
01:34:23,510 --> 01:34:25,810
Then how can mutes love?

937
01:34:38,060 --> 01:34:39,860
I love you.

938
01:34:44,800 --> 01:34:46,270
Me, too.

939
01:35:10,990 --> 01:35:13,590
We became a real couple.

940
01:35:13,830 --> 01:35:15,960
Cuz we made it down the aisle.

941
01:36:48,220 --> 01:36:50,420
Heaven's Gate Resting Place

942
01:37:09,380 --> 01:37:10,500
Wait!

943
01:37:10,580 --> 01:37:11,940
You never learn!

944
01:37:13,050 --> 01:37:14,910
How can you write
with a brain like that?

945
01:37:24,160 --> 01:37:26,560
This isn't kissing, is it?

946
01:37:38,740 --> 01:37:40,300
Can you take a picture of us?

947
01:37:40,540 --> 01:37:42,980
On three. One, two, three!

948
01:37:44,880 --> 01:37:52,950
I was born to love you.
Heaven send me to love you.

949
01:38:52,350 --> 01:38:55,320
- EUN
Won -

950
01:38:55,480 --> 01:38:57,050
I'm making noodles.
Want some?

951
01:38:57,050 --> 01:38:59,120
No, I gotta work.

952
01:38:59,120 --> 01:39:00,490
You sure?

953
01:39:00,490 --> 01:39:02,250
Yes, I'm working!

954
01:39:02,360 --> 01:39:06,350
- Then I'm just making
one! - Okay.

955
01:39:07,230 --> 01:39:09,060
Don't come beggin'later.

956
01:39:09,200 --> 01:39:11,200
- Hey!
- What?

957
01:39:11,200 --> 01:39:14,360
No eggs! Give me that.

958
01:39:16,810 --> 01:39:19,330
Wonder who invented noodles.

959
01:39:19,540 --> 01:39:22,040
You said you didn't want any.

960
01:39:22,040 --> 01:39:23,640
Changed my mind.

961
01:39:24,550 --> 01:39:26,070
Is there any rice?

962
01:39:27,880 --> 01:39:31,110
Hold on. There's
some in the fridge.

963
01:39:32,320 --> 01:39:37,380
Chul-kyu...
I'm coming to you.

964
01:39:38,730 --> 01:39:41,190
Don't worry.

965
01:39:42,300 --> 01:39:46,630
I trust you. You
were always my compass.

966
01:39:48,370 --> 01:39:53,470
Remember when I said
I can see you

967
01:39:53,470 --> 01:39:56,670
even when you're not with me?

968
01:39:58,450 --> 01:40:00,780
Go wherever you want.

969
01:40:01,750 --> 01:40:04,580
I'll find you, soon.

970
01:40:06,490 --> 01:40:10,360
Don't get mad when you see me.

971
01:40:11,830 --> 01:40:19,430
Don't ask me why I followed
you or get angry at me.

972
01:40:20,800 --> 01:40:27,830
After everything to come to
you, if you get mad I'll cry.

973
01:40:29,180 --> 01:40:34,210
When we meet again on the other
side, let's not cry again.

974
01:40:34,380 --> 01:40:37,370
Wait for me.
I'll be right there.

